            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 4186,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_017c5eCEN3gc6eoB4wxammhR\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I can see that the index.html file already has SEO meta tags, but I need to update them to better optimize for the scheduling tool. Let me improve the meta tags with:\\n\\n1. A more compelling title (under 60 characters)\\n2. A better description (150-160 characters)\\n3. Use the second image for og:image and twitter:image (the logo is already used for favicon)\\n4. Update the canonical URL placeholder\\n\\nLet me update the SEO meta tags:\"},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01M9sTZTpCj9kyjj9iVkaXs5\",\"name\":\"edit_file\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/index.html\",\"old_string\":\"    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->\\n    <title>Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams</title>\\n    <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"Automatically find meeting times across time zones. End the back-and-forth. Join 2,000+ teams who cut scheduling time by 80%. Connect calendar, share availability, done.\\\" />\\n    <link rel=\\\"canonical\\\" href=\\\"https://www.yoursite.com/\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Open Graph Meta Tags -->\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:title\\\" content=\\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:description\\\" content=\\\"Automatically find meeting times across time zones. End the back-and-forth. Join 2,000+ teams who cut scheduling time by 80%. Connect calendar, share availability, done.\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/21b36cfc-f657-471f-8256-d36bea9689fc.png\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:url\\\" content=\\\"https://www.yoursite.com/\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:type\\\" content=\\\"website\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Twitter Card Meta Tags -->\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:card\\\" content=\\\"summary_large_image\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:title\\\" content=\\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:description\\\" content=\\\"Automatically find meeting times across time zones. End the back-and-forth. Join 2,000+ teams who cut scheduling time by 80%. Connect calendar, share availability, done.\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/21b36cfc-f657-471f-8256-d36bea9689fc.png\\\" />\",\"new_string\":\"    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->\\n    <title>Auto Meeting Scheduler for Remote Teams | Time Zone Sync</title>\\n    <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"End scheduling chaos across time zones. Automatically find optimal meeting times for distributed teams. Join 2,000+ companies saving 15 hours/week. Connect & schedule instantly.\\\" />\\n    <link rel=\\\"canonical\\\" href=\\\"https://www.yoursite.com/\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Open Graph Meta Tags -->\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:title\\\" content=\\\"Auto Meeting Scheduler for Remote Teams | Time Zone Sync\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:description\\\" content=\\\"End scheduling chaos across time zones. Automatically find optimal meeting times for distributed teams. Join 2,000+ companies saving 15 hours/week. Connect & schedule instantly.\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/024dfc6c-335d-4f11-883b-f8e241f91744.png\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:url\\\" content=\\\"https://www.yoursite.com/\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:type\\\" content=\\\"website\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Twitter Card Meta Tags -->\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:card\\\" content=\\\"summary_large_image\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:title\\\" content=\\\"Auto Meeting Scheduler for Remote Teams | Time Zone Sync\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:description\\\" content=\\\"End scheduling chaos across time zones. Automatically find optimal meeting times for distributed teams. Join 2,000+ companies saving 15 hours/week. Connect & schedule instantly.\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/024dfc6c-335d-4f11-883b-f8e241f91744.png\\\" />\",\"replace_all\":false}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":10530,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":10530,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":1070,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
