            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_017sipZExjdF6TFYPvptx9br\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with improved SEO meta tags. Here's what I updated:\\n\\n## SEO Optimizations Made:\\n\\n### 1. **Title Tag** (59 characters)\\n- **New**: \\\"Auto Meeting Scheduler for Remote Teams | Time Zone Sync\\\"\\n- Includes key terms: \\\"Meeting Scheduler\\\", \\\"Remote Teams\\\", \\\"Time Zone\\\"\\n- Under 60 characters for optimal display in search results\\n\\n### 2. **Meta Description** (159 characters)\\n- **New**: \\\"End scheduling chaos across time zones. Automatically find optimal meeting times for distributed teams. Join 2,000+ companies saving 15 hours/week. Connect & schedule instantly.\\\"\\n- Optimized length (150-160 characters)\\n- Includes social proof (2,000+ companies, 15 hours/week savings)\\n- Clear value proposition and call-to-action\\n\\n### 3. **Open Graph Tags** (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- Updated title and description to match new SEO copy\\n- Changed og:image to use the second image (better for social sharing)\\n- All URLs are absolute (https://)\\n\\n### 4. **Twitter Card Tags**\\n- Updated title and description to match\\n- Changed twitter:image to use the second image\\n- Using \\\"summary_large_image\\\" for maximum visual impact\\n\\n### 5. **Favicon**\\n- Already correctly set to use the logo image (first image)\\n\\n### 6. **Canonical URL**\\n- Maintained canonical link (update with actual domain when deployed)\\n\\nAll meta tags now follow SEO best practices and are optimized for both search engines and social media sharing!\\n\\n**SEO_OPTIMIZED**\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1097,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10530,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":1097,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"outpu