            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01BCpFTTACdCN6cFB7oFABRR\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with comprehensive SEO meta tags. Here's what I added:\\n\\n## SEO Optimization Summary:\\n\\n### Basic SEO\\n- **Title**: \\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" (58 characters - under 60 limit)\\n- **Meta Description**: Compelling 155-character description highlighting the pain point (scheduling chaos), solution (instant optimal times), and social proof (2,000+ companies, 15 hours/week saved)\\n- **Canonical URL**: Added for proper indexing\\n\\n### Open Graph Tags (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- All required OG tags including type, URL, title, description\\n- **OG Image**: Using the second image (not the logo) for better social media preview\\n- Ensures rich previews when shared on social platforms\\n\\n### Twitter Card Tags\\n- Summary large image card for maximum visual impact\\n- Matching title and description for consistency\\n- Same preview image as Open Graph\\n\\n### Favicon\\n- Updated to use the logo image (first image) with absolute URL\\n- Ensures brand consistency across browser tabs\\n\\n### Key Features:\\n✅ All URLs are absolute (https://)\\n✅ Title under 60 characters\\n✅ Description at 155 characters (optimal for search results)\\n✅ Copy emphasizes pain points (scheduling chaos, time zones) and benefits (instant, saves time)\\n✅ Includes social proof (2,000+ teams, 15 hours/week savings)\\n✅ Target audience clearly addressed (distributed teams, remote companies)\\n\\nSEO_OPTIMIZED\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":985,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":9972,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":985,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":357,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
