            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01DhCjFWjk2HFMbDQyNg4Hja\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with comprehensive SEO meta tags. Here's what I added:\\n\\n## SEO Optimizations Applied:\\n\\n### Basic SEO\\n- **Title**: \\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" (59 characters - under 60 limit)\\n- **Meta Description**: Compelling 155-character description highlighting the key benefit (eliminating scheduling chaos) and social proof (save 15+ hours per week)\\n- **Canonical URL**: Added for proper indexing\\n\\n### Open Graph Tags (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- og:type, og:url, og:title, og:description\\n- og:image using the second image (the non-logo image for better social sharing)\\n\\n### Twitter Card Tags\\n- twitter:card set to \\\"summary_large_image\\\" for maximum visual impact\\n- All required Twitter meta tags with consistent messaging\\n\\n### Favicon\\n- Updated to use the logo image with absolute URL\\n\\n### Key Features:\\n✅ All URLs are absolute (https://)\\n✅ Title under 60 characters\\n✅ Description at 155 characters (optimal for search results)\\n✅ Compelling copy focused on pain points (scheduling chaos, time zones) and benefits (save time)\\n✅ Used logo for favicon and feature image for social sharing\\n✅ Consistent messaging across all platforms\\n\\nSEO_OPTIMIZED\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":984,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10010,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":984,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":311,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
